entry.title: Fall 2024 schedule for DH Co-Op
entry.content: The DH Co-Op will begin holding its regular meetings on Tuesday, September 24 from 1:30-4:30 PM, and Wednesday, September 25 from 12-1:30 PM. Meetings will be held this quarter through Wednesday, November 6th. A detailed schedule of activtiies and workshops will be posted soon.
